model - The model of the airplane

cruiseSpeed - The speed at which the airplane cruises
flightPlan - The FlightPlan from which this Airplane was instantiated

Updates the range of this Airplane according to its tank size, cruise speed, and liters per hour ratio.

                           Hour

 let cruiseSpeed := n Knots = 1.852 * n -----------
                                          Hour

 let litersPerHour := z --------
                          Hour

       =  --- Hours * (1.852 * n) ------------
